gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Heye priti Hari mainh ghani, shun kahie motyap baiyot tani;
Tenek divas mozar, thai pushpani vristi apar.

Here is the translation:

Then after that, Amba Bai, I was with my mind in that samadhi; 
I left it there with what, one beautiful evening sun.

Here is the translation:

This is Jamunabai's home, Hari comes every day and makes it great; 
One Sonibai is a devotee of God, her name is Parvati, she is auspicious.

Here is the translation:

A thamboli in a basket is mine, Jamunabai's name is; 
It will get understood always with God at His place, He makes that entry.
